snippet.title: Sneek Peak inside 'Piko Interactive Collection 1' manual for Evercade
snippet.description:
A look inside the manual for the 'Piko Interactive Collection 1' cartridge: 
https://evercade.co.uk/piko-interactive-collection-1-cartridge/

Full games list:
1. Brave Battle Saga
2. Water Margin
3. Magic Girl
4. Dorke and Ymp
5. Switchblade
6. Way of the exploding fist
7. NightShade
8. Top Racer
9. Tinhead
10. Radical Rex
11. Jim Power – The Lost Dimension
12. 8-Eyes
13. The Immortal
14. Dragon View
15. Drakkhen
16. Power Punch II
17. Power Piggs of the Dark Ages
18. Iron Commando
19. The Humans
20. Canon – Legends of the New Gods
